keyFacts: A signed unsealing order for Ghislaine Maxwell was issued on July 2, 2020.
The order was signed by United States Magistrate Judge Katharine Parker of the Southern District of New York.
The document is an email forwarding the order, indicating it was part of legal correspondence and procedure.
